*.jpg   binary
*.jpeg  binary
*.JPG   binary
*.JPEG  binary
*.PNG   binary
*.gif   binary
*.webp  binary
*.avif  binary
*.ico   binary
*.pdf   binary
*.woff  binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf   binary
*.otf   binary
